        <description><p><a href="https://www.drupal.org/project/reroute_email">Reroute Email</a> module uses <code>hook_mail_alter()</code> to prevent emails from being sent to users from non-production sites. It allows you to enter one or more email addresses that will receive the emails instead of delivering them to the original user.</p>
